* Paston-Williams, Sara (2006) &quot;Fish: Recipes from a Busy Island&quot; Page 132, National Trust Books. .
* Sweetser, Wendy (2009) &quot;The Connoisseur&#x27;s Guide to Fish &amp; Seafood&quot; Page 194, Sterling Publishing Company. .

