where formula_21 is the Alfvén velocity. With the above relations, the dimensionless reconnection rate formula_22 can then be written in two forms, the first in terms of formula_23 using the result earlier derived from Ohm&#x27;s law, the second in terms of formula_24 from the conservation of mass as
