<doc id="1166800" wikidata="Q2010944" url="?curid=1166800" title="Conceição, Paraíba">
<text>Conceição is a municipality &quot;(município)&quot; in the state of Paraíba in Brazil. The population is 19,007 (2020 est.) in an area of 579 km2. It is part of the microregion of Itaporanga.

